## 🚀 Technology Stack (Proposed)

### Frontend
- React.js / Next.js
- Redux for state management
- Tailwind CSS / Material-UI
- Progressive Web App (PWA)

### Backend
- Node.js with Express / Django / Spring Boot
- RESTful API / GraphQL
- JWT authentication

### Database
- PostgreSQL (primary)
- Redis (caching)
- MongoDB (product catalog - optional)

### Payment Integration
- Stripe / Razorpay / PayPal
- Payment gateway SDK

### Infrastructure
- AWS / Google Cloud / Azure
- Docker & Kubernetes
- CI/CD with GitHub Actions

